# OpenAPI Generator Ignore
#
# Files listed here are NOT overwritten by `./generate`. See:
# https://openapi-generator.tech/docs/customization/#ignore-file-format

# Project documentation we maintain by hand
README.md

# CI / repo housekeeping we own
.travis.yml
.gitignore
git_push.sh

# go.mod / go.sum: managed via dependabot + go mod tidy. v7's go.mod.mustache
# regenerates these with stale dependency versions and the wrong Go version.
go.mod
go.sum

# v7 emits auto-stub test files under test/ that just compare an empty client
# against the real API. We have our own hand-written tests at the repo root
# (client_test.go, configuration_test.go, response_test.go, api_commits_test.go)
# which actually exercise the code we care about.
test/**
